Tugas_rancang_PAM INFOGRAPHICS APPLICATION //page home Welcome to Gembira Loka Zoo service Find our various fauna collection such as mammals, reptilia, aves, amphibi, pisces. //page information ATTRACTION MAPS GALLERY RECREATION //page recreation Onta Tunggang Visitors can enjoy riding camel rides that cross in the desert typical of the Middle East while taking pictures in front of the pyramid. Petting Zoo Visitors can freely interact and become a place to introduce animals to children in particular and society in general. Zoo Express Mini trains consisting of 2 (two) passenger cars where each cart can carry 12 children or 8-10 adults. Ninebot Ninebot or Smart Wheels is a kind of Self Balancing Electric Scooter that can be controlled by both adults and children. Kolam Sentuh Touch various types of fish and various other aquatic animals that are a collection of Gembira Loka Zoo. Gajah Tunggang Feel the ride of the largest mammal on ground, slowly walking on the arena. Kolam Tangkap This facility has a pool that is only 30cm deep which contains small fish for children to catch. Terapi Ikan Therapy is becoming a trend in a number of countries including Indonesia, now in the Gembira Loka Zoo. Perahu Kayuh Go around the pool using this goose-shaped paddle boat. Skuter Air This water vehicle is indeed similar to Jet Sky, the difference is that this water scooter is operated in an artificial pond in the Gembira Loka Zoo. Taring Gembira Loka Zoo has presented TARING (Mobile Transportation) which will help visitors to interesting places that they want to visit. ATV ATV rides are also in Gembira Loka Zoo, feel the thrill of riding this four-wheeled motorcycle. Bumper Boat Enjoy the sensation of circling around the pool and colliding with one another with a Bumper boat. Speed Boat The only speedboat that runs in the middle of the city of Yogyakarta. Perahu Katamaran Riding this Catamaran Boat you can surround an artificial lake with beautiful views.
